            <thetext>Steps to reproduce:

1. Select a widget with child controls like a &quot;qx.ui.window.Window&quot;
2. Select a child control e.g. the titlebar widget
3. Check the value for the &quot;appearance&quot; property

This value should be the generated id for the child control like &quot;window/titlebar-label&quot; and not just &quot;label&quot;.

The issue here is, that the default value for the appearance property ar shown and not the generated ones used within the appearance theme.</thetext>
